Gala Coral’s Former Boss Bids for Bingo Business, Mail Reports

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-03-27T14:24:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-27/gala-coral-s-former-boss-bids-for-bingo-business-mail-reports.html
Gala Coral Group Ltd.’s former
chairman, John Kelly, is seeking to buy the company’s bingo
business, the  Mail on Sunday  said, without saying where it got
the information.  Kelly has been rebuffed on price, the newspaper reported.
Rank Group Plc is considering a bid, the newspaper said, without
giving any further details.’  To contact the reporter on this story:
